== Grammar ==

When they stand alone, い-adjectives don't take the copula, but when modifying nouns, they do. Otherwise they don't change.

{| class="wikitable"
| colspan=2 | <い-adjective>
|-
| rowspan=2 | <い-adjective> <noun> || です
|-
| だ
|}

